subject: Basketball (College)
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: Undermanned Rutgers managed to tie the score at 45-45 with six minutes remaining, but Maryland needed all of 2 minutes 23 seconds to push its lead back to 8 and extinguish any hope of an upset.
